rows.label: qst711001_msg0001
rows.name:
What do you think? Of this flagship,
built with the best of our Superbian
Empire's technology?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0003
rows.name:
The only downside is that
it's too high-spec, which
makes us mechanics cry.

rows.label: qst711001_msg0004
rows.name:
Every time we anchor in port, we're
so busy with maintenance... I haven't
been home in a long time.

rows.label: qst711001_msg0005
rows.name:
When you spend a long time flying
all over Alst with the flagship, you
start to miss the taste of home.

rows.label: qst711001_msg0006
rows.name:
I tried to make a recipe my
mother taught me from memory,
but it didn't turn out well...

rows.label: qst711001_msg0007
rows.name:
That's it! Is there anyone
among you who can cook?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0008
rows.name:
I'll teach you the recipe, so
could you please make me a dish
from my hometown, Chilsain?

rows.label: qst711001_msg0009
rows.name:
Well then, I'll be
looking forward to it!
